### Randomizer API - REST Client Tests
### Make sure the server is running: make run

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

###############################################################################
# Random Playground Endpoints
###############################################################################

### 1. Home - Welcome endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/ HTTP/1.1

### 2. Generate random number (1 to max_value)
GET {{baseUrl}}/random/100 HTTP/1.1

### 3. Generate random number with small max
GET {{baseUrl}}/random/10 HTTP/1.1

### 4. Generate random number between min and max
GET {{baseUrl}}/random-between?min_value=1&max_value=99 HTTP/1.1

### 5. Random between with custom range
GET {{baseUrl}}/random-between?min_value=50&max_value=200 HTTP/1.1

### 6. Random between with boundaries
GET {{baseUrl}}/random-between?min_value=1&max_value=1000 HTTP/1.1

